So we want something to make it dynamic and we will pass a variable like openjdk-21-version: 1.22-1.1749462973 in our Gitlab and it should take it from the variable that value and update it while building teh images in pipeline....i am also sharing the build stage configuration to you ....please check and suggest the best possible solution....

